User manual 

Files are submitted to main.sh 

Format of submission is 

bash main.sh ./geometries/*filename* *name for the folder of final data* 

make_geom.sh - makes the displaced geometries in the ./input_geometries  folder 
Each atom is a separate folder with multiple folders corresponding to the displacement in atoms.

run_gaussian.job arg_1="absolute path to the file"

From the folder electric_field/files takes the input files and copies them to the corresponding folders
and then submits the job to the gaussian
